{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2e4350c980","title":"中共中央、国务院、中央军委、中央文革关于播送林彪同志讲话录音的通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"fb7a527e86","index":0,"year":1967,"month":4,"day":7,"articleId":"2e4350c980","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"军队和军事","id":"6f7a683373","type":"主题"},{"name":"中共中央、国务院、中央军委、中央文革联发","id":"cbee4acb80","type":"发行机构"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"中央文件","id":"ef6e778547","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"84c6637233","type":"title","text":"中共中央、国务院、中央军委、中央文革关于播送林彪同志讲话录音的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2e4350c980","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f3fde477ba","type":"paragraph","text":"我们伟大领袖毛主席指示，林彪同志一九六七年三月二十日讲话录音，应向中国人民解放军人员和全国红卫兵播放。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2e4350c980","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c1c0e3cf35","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪同志的讲话，是一个极其重要的马克思列宁主义、毛泽东思想的报告，对指导当前的无产阶级文化大革命运动，指导人民解放军正确地介入地方无产阶级文化大革命，推动无产阶级革命派在两条路线的斗争中进一步取得胜利，具有非常重大的意义。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2e4350c980","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9cddcfaf13","type":"paragraph","text":"各军区党委，各级党委、各省、市革命委员会，各军事管制委员会，各革命群众组织必须认真组织大家学习林彪同志讲话，坚决贯彻执行。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2e4350c980","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0d53a36ead","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2e4350c980","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fbcd2005d3","type":"paragraph","text":"国 务 院","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2e4350c980","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8932672a85","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央军委","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2e4350c980","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"77e07ecacd","type":"paragraph","text":"中央文革小组","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2e4350c980","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4ecb90ad3f","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六七年四月七日","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2e4350c980","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}